name: Off the Dock - Low Tide Sunrise
description: When the moon is full, the tides reach the most extremes. The reef's edge can be seen when the tide is at its lowest. The Sun rises on the 24th of June, 2021 just behind the Kaneohe Marine Base. To its left, is coconut island with the great pacific ocean behind it. This is a piece of a collection started on OpenSea and now making its entrance on H=N.
